    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019ve got something truly special for you today. This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just stepped out of a time capsule. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, pampered with hand-washes only\u2014it\u2019s in that pristine condition we all dream of finding. There\u2019s a tiny, barely-there mark near the door handle that you\u2019d probably never notice, but I like to be upfront! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' feel. I'm only letting her go to make some room in the garage for a new project, so I\u2019m hoping to find a buyer who will cherish this gem as much as I have. Come by and see it; I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
